<subSubSection id="46746CC8125D41B567B5810A0BD693AA" pageId="null" pageNumber="602" type="vernacular_names">
<paragraph id="1862BF2C763D9389068DDBC445060CC2" pageId="null" pageNumber="602">Dichtbehaarte Platterbse</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="4FE67D5889973B247610015E596E4C55" pageId="null" pageNumber="602" type="description">
<paragraph id="67E39CED33291A898A871A400DD42734" pageId="null" pageNumber="602">
<emphasis id="E27DBEC8C9782F123E05354166E3219A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="602">Pflanze</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="636E1ED664CE30BC8DFF83D21A52F359" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="602">auch Kelch und Frucht</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis id="EE7639C2702ED912DFCD58FA1433192D" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="602">
dicht behaart. Kelch etwa 4 mm lang; 
<normalizedToken id="317187FA21F6C4EC647A9E9E4ACC2797" originalValue="längere" pageId="null" pageNumber="602">laengere</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="4D17779B2233585CF35BA2E84C930BBD" originalValue="Kelchzähne" pageId="null" pageNumber="602">Kelchzaehne</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="4281A126A9DBC89C7A3FD5C00D20A730" originalValue="½" pageId="null" pageNumber="602">1/2</normalizedToken>
-⅔ 
<emphasis id="06E60D2CD36273D2713E4C9977383BA4" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="602">
so lang wie die 
<normalizedToken id="42334347AA70FAEDB777A91F334AEBEE" originalValue="Kelchröhre" pageId="null" pageNumber="602">Kelchroehre</normalizedToken>
.
</emphasis>
Krone 1-1,4 cm lang. Frucht 2-2,5 cm lang und 0,4-0,5 cm breit. - 
<normalizedToken id="E867C509C5A62609DD3B4D80E2EE2FD6" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="602">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="30EA89BBDAB4780627819F50CB4C7897" pageId="null" pageNumber="602">
<emphasis id="EA3A0A1ECA377A52879A785689826C15" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="602">
<pageBreakToken id="CB9A6D7A161A3604597ACAADF55D0D24" pageId="null" pageNumber="602">Zytologische</pageBreakToken>
Angaben.
</emphasis>
Keine Untersuchungen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="31BC73B1927003CDFA22EC1BC806DF6C" pageId="null" pageNumber="602">
<emphasis id="A678CA2C6609D8692EEFF282F57A95BD" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="602">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin und montan, seltener subalpin. Trockene 
<normalizedToken id="AF1393C71D33777AE5D509BEE8E621EA" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="602">Boeden</normalizedToken>
in warmen Lagen. Trockenwiesen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="9FA80E20A66C83120DD7B16DFD430D74" pageId="null" pageNumber="602">
<emphasis id="9DB468EC8DEC324E264E5F659CCDDAA1" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="602">Verbreitung.</emphasis>
Nicht genau bekannt. - Im Gebiet: Savoyen, Rhonetal vom Genfersee 
<normalizedToken id="8EDB1628B25C95B4AAAD19D46B2CCDC8" originalValue="aufwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="602">aufwaerts</normalizedToken>
, Aostatal, Vintschgau (Glurns); ziemlich selten.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
